         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">15/11/86 ¶  ¶ By this post I am sending you, noble Friend, two packets of algae that Mr Bracebridge Wilson recently brought together and entrusted to me to forward. Please write me a few lines when th...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">86.11.15a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. <seg style="">Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund, Sweden.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">15/11/86</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit dieser Post sende ich Ihnen, edler Freund, zwei Packete Algen, welche Mr Bracebr. Wilson in letzterer Zeit zusammenbrachte und mir zur Weitersendung anvertraute. Bitte, schreiben Sie mir ein paar Reihen, wenn die Päckchen ankommen, da ich dann aus Verantwortung bin.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Immer</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Ich habe jetzt </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">grosse</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Exemplare von Claudea Bennett. in Aussicht, u hoffe dass </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Frucht</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> daran ist. Wie gesagt, ich möchte diese Alge, wenn das Genus wirklich neu ist, mit Ihnen <name key="Sonderia">Sonderia</name> nennen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Eben geht mir eine <name key="Grevillea">Grevillea</name> mit bicarpellaren Blumen zu; apocarpische Frucht war bei den Proteaceen noch nicht beobachtet.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">15/11/86</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By this post I am sending you, noble Friend, two packets of algae that Mr Bracebridge Wilson recently brought together and entrusted to me to forward. Please write me a few lines when the little parcels arrive, because I am then free of responsibility.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Always</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I now have prospects of <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">large</hi>
               </seg> specimens of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Claudea%20bennettiana">Claudea bennettiana</name>
               </seg> and hope that <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">fruit</hi>
               </seg> is on them. As stated<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M to J. Agardh, 14 October 1886 (in this edition as 86-10-14a).</p>
               </note> I would like to name this alga with you, if the genus really is new, <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Sonderia">Sonderia</name>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Grevillea">Grevillea</name>
               </seg> has just reached me with bicarpellate flowers; apocarpous fruit were not yet observed in the <name key="Proteaceae">Proteaceae</name>.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Claudea%20bennettiana">Claudea bennettiana</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Grevillea">Grevillea</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Proteaceae">Proteaceae</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Sonderia">Sonderia</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
